data.title: Bitcoin Price to $100K or $80K as Matrixport Predicts Bulls-Bears Impasse?
data.description: Bitcoin price has just entered a rare zone of impasse between bulls and bears, according to crypto market expert Matrixport. Traders are noticing a stalemate between both bullish and bearish sentiments, prompting debate on whether Bitcoin price to rally towards $100K or crash to $80K. Bitcoin Price Direction in Limbo Amid Major Market Shift Thanksgiving
data.keywords: Bitcoin price, options traders, BTC price, Bitcoin Price Direction, market shift
